  <description>
    <p>
      Bruno is a Fast and Git-Friendly API client. Bruno stores your collections directly in a folder on your filesystem. We use a plain text markup language, Bru, to save information about API requests.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Stores your collections in a folder on your filesystem</li>
      <li>Use git for collaboration </li>
      <li>No cloud sync. Fully offline.</li>
      <li>Majority of our features are free and have been opensourced under the MIT license. See: https://github.com/usebruno/bruno</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

